    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. It\u2019s been well-cared for, runs like a dream, and is just waiting for someone new to take it on some fun adventures! If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road, this is the one for you. Let me know if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
