    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six power unit. This high-revving engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain consists of a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a recent valve clearance adjustment (Shim kit). The chassis remains composed with refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, maintaining the car's celebrated turn-in response. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping and light patina consistent with a well-enjoyed driver, the mechanical integrity is excellent. A comprehensive cooling system overhaul and rod bearing inspection provide peace of mind for the next enthusiast owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
