    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable driver that still turns heads. The exterior is finished in a lustrous metallic paint that retains a deep shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical marks of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free. The upholstery shows light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, but the stitching remains tight and the leather supple. All onboard electronics, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with a consistent idle, backed by a comprehensive service history that confirms regular oil changes and preventative maintenance. The transmission shifts crisply, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. Recently fitted with a set of high-performance all-season tires, this car is mechanically sound and ready for immediate delivery. It offers the perfect blend of sophisticated style and dependable performance for the discerning driver.",
